      "heading": null,
      "description": "Make the Poached Chicken &amp; Ginger Broth."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Cook the noodles following pack instructions. Drain and rinse under cold water until completely cool. Set aside."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Shred the chicken and set aside. Peel the carrots and julienne both them and the cucumber into matchsticks. Thinly slice the spring onions and roughly chop the coriander."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "In a small bowl, whisk together the soy sauce, rice vinegar and chilli crisp. Taste and tweak with a pinch of salt if needed."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "In a large bowl, toss the noodles with the dressing. Add the shredded chicken, carrots and cucumber. Give everything a gentle mix."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Top with spring onions, coriander and sesame seeds. Serve cold or at room temp."
